result.name: Carbone Hong Kong

reviews.text: Carbone is undoubtedly one of my top 5 restaurants in Hong Kong. The service is impeccable, the best I’ve witnessed on a consistent basis (shout-out to Jack and his team). Food is great as well, love the desserts (tiramisu especially)! Together with its fun vibe, Carbone is a perfect place to have a great weekend or special evening.
Great room for a large group. Excellent service and staff. Fantastic desserts

The spicy rigatoni which is the signature pasta is so rich in taste w just the right level of chewiness, it's simply amazing.  I ordered the carrot cake w ginger ice cream, and again the cake so rich n full of flavor that my only reaction was wow.  😅
Excellent environment and service.  Attractive lunch and lower price than dinner. Worth to try.
Amazing service! Great food. Warning - don't fill up on the bread! The dessert portions are huge. The main dishes are just enough for one.
